<beginEffectRule>
IncreaseProgressCurrentFUR
-1
WorkOnFUR
0
false
true
<beginRuleAnnotation>
Increases progress on sizing the next Functional User Requirement, determined by the employees' Average Time Spent on Functional User Requirements, which is influenced by their level of expertise (Major, Intermediate, or Minor). The progress is also adjusted based on factors such as the employee's profile, the quality and extent of documentation, the complexity or number of FUR, and whether tools are being used effectively.
<endRuleAnnotation>
<beginParticipantRuleEffect>
